(33, 'sambatra', 'Sambatra.....â™ªâ™ª\\n\\n Na dia manonja aza ny alondrano ety\\n Ianao ry Ray no mitanana ahy\\n Ho sasa-poana reo mpanenjika ahy ety !\\n Tsisy maharesy anao!\\n\\n Ref:\\n Misosa mora na be mpanakora Ity sambokeliko\\n Fa miandry ahy ilay Salema vao!\\n Na fijaliana ,na fahoriana no iainako ety \\n Tsy ho kivy aho satria\\n Tsy ho kivy aho satria\\n AMPY AHY NY FAHASOAVANAO\\n Tsy izaho irery no miaina toy izany\\n F\'ianao koa mety mitomany\\n Tsarovy anefa fa Jesosy tsy mandao!\\n mibitsika ao amponao ao!!\\n\\n Ref:.... Vonana ve ianao?\\n Ny handray Azy zao\\n Mba ho Tompo sy Mpamonjy anao....\\n Refrain (â†—cle) (tapitra) fin'),
(34, 'Annie jaspienne', 'IZY IRERY\\n\\n 1)Mampisava izany foko tsy ho kivy\\n Ny fisian\'i Jeso lay mpamonjiko\\n Mampahery,manatanjaka ny foko\\n Ny fitiavany sy famindram_pony\\n\\n 2)Ny olana izay miseho amin\'ny fiainako\\n Izy no mamaha izany rehetra izany\\n Ireo fahoriana izay mianjady amiko\\n Eo anilako Jeso manampy ahy\\n\\n 3)Ny ho aviko dia feno fifaliana\\n Satria Jeso tsy misaraka amiko\\n Izy dia manomana fiainam_baovao\\n Izay feno fahasambarana tokoa\\n\\n Refrain:\\n Izy irery no iankihinako izao\\n Sy omeko izany fo\\n Tsisy zavatra izay, atakaloko Azy\\n Satria Izy efa namoy ny ainy hamonjy ahy\\n ANNIE JASPIENNE\\n(tapitra) fin'),
(35, 'LAMBA SOA', 'LAMBA SOA\\n\\n 1)Lambam_pahamarinana\\n Fotsy sady madio no atafy re\\n Izay mibebaka tokoa,miova fo\\n Miala @ ota izao\\n N\'iza n\'iza te handray\\n Dia omena tsotr\'izao\\n Raha toa mendrika\\n Lambam_pahamarinana\\n Notenonina tamin\'ilay rÃ n\'i Jeso be fitia\\n\\n Refrain:\\n (Lamba soa)*2 mendrika\\n Maharakotra tokoa sy madio\\n (No omena)*2 ho ahy sy ho anao\\n Tsy vidiana fa omen\'ny Tompo anao\\n\\n 2)Irianao ve ry sakaiza\\n Ny ho tafian\'i Jeso tia ilay lamba madio\\n Izay tsy ronta fa mateza\\n Mendrika anao, maharakotra anao\\n Ndeha hanatona any koa\\n Sy hibebaka Aminy\\n Ka ekeo ny otanao\\n F\'Izy hamela heloka\\n Hanadio anao\\n Ka hanafy anao ilay fitafiana vao\\n\\n Refrain:\\n (Lamba soa)*2.......\\n Io no fitafian\'ny (lanitra ery)*2\\n Izay rehetra te hakao (dia mankery)*2\\n Amin\'ny hazo fijaliana\\n Eo Jeso no hizara izany\\n Izay tsy manana tsy mba hiditra ao\\n Refrain:\\n\\n (Lamba soa)*2.....\\n\\n ANNIE JASPIENNE\\n (tapitra) fin'),
(36, 'Tsy_foiny ', 'Tsy_foiny \\n\\n (*2)Tsy foiny ho very aho,fa nantsoiny ihany\\n Na be ireo ratsy vita toa sesy lany \\n Izay nalehako toa nombany hatrany \\n Izaho kosa,toa ninia tsy namaly\\n\\n Ref: Midera Anao ny foko\\n Ihira ho Anao ry Tompo\\n Fa Ianao ilay mpitahiry\\n Ny fanahiko\\n Herezonao fa malemy\\n Arovy koa,tsy ho very\\n Ianao irery Tompo\\n no hany heriko\\n Mitempo mangina izany antsonao\\n Tsy nisy nahasakana ahy fa mahery Ianao\\n Tsy noesorinao tamiko ny fitiavanao\\n Inty aho ry Tompo\\n Raiso ho Anao\\n (tapitra) fin'),
(37, 'Ny Lasa Namonjeny', 'NY LASA NAMONJENY\\n\\n  1)Tsy misy atahorana ny ho avy \\n Mitranga eo anatrehanao \\n Raha toa ka tsaroanao ny lasa \\n Zay namonjeny Tompo anao \\n Aoka ho tadidinao \\n Fa tanana mahery no efa teo \\n Miharo sy mitahy \\n Teo anoloan\'ny loza be nanjo\\n  K\'aza milofika \\n Ny fonao mahereza re anio \\n Tadidio fa Jeso \\n Miara_mitomany aminao\\n\\n  ref:\\n  Tsy ho mora anie \\n Ny fisedrana izay hahazo anao\\n Fa mila mahatoky hatr@ farany \\n Vao miara_monina @jeso \\n Aoka ho fantatrao\\n Tsia tsy oran_dranomasin a fitaratra \\n Ireo zay tsy nandalo \\n Fahorian_dehibe  \\n Mba mifampivavaha ho tody sao\\n\\n  2)Nadaboky ny fahafatesana \\n Ilay olona malalanao \\n Nangina tsy niloabava ianao \\n Fa loza be sy hatambo izao \\n Ety an_tany no ahitanao \\n Fahoriana lehibe \\n Nefa matokia \\n Ny Tompo efa niteny hoe \\n Hiaro anao \\n Mandalo ihany anie \\n Zao loza izay mitranga izao \\n Ka Dia\\n Aoka ianao hahatsiahy  Reo lasa namonjeny Tompo anao\\n\\n Mr VONJY sy GROUPE Nosy\\n  tapitra fin'),
