(41, 'fondreny', 'âž¡Fon_dReny â¬…\\n\\n 1) Raha maditra ny zanaka\\n Dia mampibaby fahoriana\\n Ny ngidim-po sy ranomaso\\n No mameno ny ao am-po\\n Ilay nitondra folo volana\\n Nitia, nitaiza , sy nanabe\\n Nizaka ny mafaitra indrindra\\n Nitaintaina sy nangovitra \\n Nefa na diso fanantenana\\n Tsy very toky fa miandrandra\\n Ilay Nahary Lehibe\\n Hamerin-doha an-janany e!\\n\\n ref:\\n Nefa ny fon\'ny Reny (*2)\\n Feno fitiavana an-janany\\n Na dia nania ireny (*2)\\n Tiny hiverina an-tratrany\\n Tsy vali-babena no iriny\\n Fa ny fiainanao tsy hisy tsiny\\n Tena finaritra miadana\\n Eny ny fijaliana fiafiana\\n Mitrosina resy fahoriana\\n Tsy tiany hanody an-janany\\n Nefa na jamba sady kilemaina \\n Maona marenina farofy lava\\n Tiany satria izay no anjarany\\n\\n 2) Ny zaza hendry maha te ho tia \\n Dia mirana ny sainy faly ery\\n Fa tsy nandratra azy ireny\\n Tsy nanadino ny anatra omeny\\n Adino tokoa izay manjo\\n Ny taranany hendry tokoa\\n Tsy fola-damosina foana i Neny\\n Tsy fotsy rora raha niteny\\n Ry menaky ny aina naloaka ny kibo\\n Tsarovy i Neny, eny tsiahivo\\n Teny antitra sy votsy volo\\n Tia ahy izy fa nikolo\\n\\n Refrain..........\\n 3)Indraindray ny lehilahy\\n Mandositra ny tokantranony\\n Avelany eo izy hijaly \\n Hamelon-drery ny ankohonany\\n I Neny kosa mba ho aiza moa???\\n Mibaby sy mitrotro, miloloha\\n Adidy izay mavesatra indrindra\\n Nisikina izy, nizaka ny mangidy\\n Koboniny am-po tsy miloaka\\n Ny alahelo ny Ray izay nitsoaka\\n Ny vavaka ataony mafy hoe:\\n \"Ny zanany mba ho hendry e!\"\\n\\n Refrain............\\n Tapitra fin'),
(42, 'DOLIFA', 'Raha zay vavan\'olona\\n Na zay resak\'olona\\n Aza atao hisakana tsy hiangonana\\n Raha izay henatr\'olona\\n Na ny tsy fanana\\n Aza ho fialana tsy hivavahana\\n\\n Ref:Tiany ianao e(2*)\\n Tia ahy Jesosy\\n Tia antsika\\n Raha zay volon-koditra\\n Ny tsy fitoviana koa\\n Aza atao hefitra mandratra fo\\n Raha zay fifandirana\\n Disadisa ady lava\\n Aza mampiverina sao nenina\\n\\n Ref\\n\\n Raha iza mpanenjika\\n Mbola mety ho rendrika\\n Koa ataovy kosa izay\\n Maha-mendrika\\n Fa tsy sitrak\'i Tsitoha\\n Izay tsy mba mankatoa\\n Aoka ho mpanompo tena mahasoa\\n\\n Ref\\n DOLIFA\\n tapitra fin'),
(43, 'RAHA AO AM_POKO G.Hiraina(Fanasina)', 'RAHA AO AM_POKO \\n\\n 1)Raha ao am_poko ao\\n No itoeranao mba ho lapanao\\n Ka havaozinao indray\\n Toa ilay Edena hatrizay\\n Dia ho rava sy hikoro\\n Ilay fanjakan\'ny haizina taloha\\n Fa mazava no hasolo\\n Sy honina ao tokoa\\n\\n Refrain:\\n Izany Ray no hetahetan\'ny fo mila Anao\\n Dia Ianao hitoetra lalina ao anatiko ao\\n Na rahoviana io ry Tompo tsy ho lany\\n Satria manana Anao ilay Ray tsy mba mandao\\n Fifaliana,fihobiana hatrany\\n No hameno azy mandrakizay\\n\\n 2)Reo ady hatrizay\\n Dia handositra ka tsy ho hita ao\\n Fa fandresena indray\\n No hanjaka ao rahatrizay\\n G.Hiraina(Fanasina)\\n'),
(44, 'Paoly sy Izaho Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ ', 'Paoly sy Izaho\\n\\n  Antaonany maro\\n Nanenjehako anao\\n Ela ny ela e hitako ianao\\n Hitako ianao tao damaskosy\\n Hay ianao re ianao no Jesosy\\n\\n ref;\\n Jamba ny masoko\\n Nikipy aho taloha\\n Nihiratra aho nihaona taminao\\n Nitorabato koa ireo zay nino anao\\n Ankehitriny vao nahita anao\\n  Ela ny ela e hitako ianao hitako ianao tao \\ndamaskosy\\n Efa ela koa nitadiavako anao\\n Ela ny ela e hitako ianao\\n Ny baiboly no manambara\\n Hay Ianao re lay Tompo tsara\\n\\n   Jamba ny masoko\\n nikipy aho taloha\\n Nihiratra aho nihaona taminao\\n Nitorabato koa ireo zay nino anao\\n Ankehitriny vao nahita anao\\n  Ny baiboly no manambara fa ianao re\\n Lay Tompo tsara\\n Ory mpanota mbola variana\\n Raha mifanena e @ Jeso\\n Mba hialao re ny haratsiana\\n Ka miova re fa ho vonjeny\\n  Jamba ianao taloha\\n Nikipy ihany koa\\n Ankehitriny nahita anao Tompo soa\\n Hanova anao tokoa ny fiaonan aminy\\n Ario ny ratsy vitanao taloha\\n Mba hialao re ny haratsiana\\n Ka miova re fa ho vonjeny\\n tapitra fin'),
(45, 'Mila famonjena Fanaf', '~~Mila famonjena~~\\n\\n  Ry Ray mahery jereo ny taninay\\n Fa feno tsilo sy hery manepotra ny fiiainanay\\n Ety no ahitam-pahoriana tsy misy fiadanana\\n Ianao no nandavorary no manam-panafana\\n Ry Jeso Ã´, o jereo ny ondrinao\\n Aza avelanao hiady irery \\n Fa fefika re izahay\\n Ampio sy kolokoloy\\n Izay miankina aminao \\n Fa ny eo aminao fifaliana ka lafatra ny fiainanay\\n\\n  Ref:Ety,ety feno korontana\\n Eo aminao no hiadanako\\n Jereo,jereo ity tany honenanay \\n Fa miady lava mifandrotika\\n Henoy,henoy zao antsoko izao\\n O mba valio ho fitsaharana\\n Ekeo,ekeo zao vavako izao fa mila famonjena \\nizahay.....\\n\\n   Korontana sy tebiteby\\n Areti-mandringana\\n Ety maro mpandrebireby o\\n Sy mpamingapingana\\n Feno mpifosafosa\\n Sy mpanendrikendrika\\n Fiainana mandratra fo\\n O tsy misy fiadanana\\n Ry Jeso o,o jereo ny ondrinao\\n Fa maro no miady lava sy mifandramatra\\n Avoty amin\'ny sandry mahery\\n Fa mila ho rendrika\\n Ampianaro mitia Ray mahery o\\n Ho ravaky ny fiainana\\n Ref\\n FANAF\\n'),
