(53, 'fitia safononoka', 'FITIA SAFONONOKA\\n\\n  1)Mahatsiaro karakaina ao anatiko ao\\n Vesaran_keloka,hafanam_po no natao\\n Mahatsiaro toa mangidy fa lavitra Anao\\n Toa olo_manjenjena aho izao\\n Fantatro fa feno ny fitiavanao ahy\\n Kanefa dia nolaviko ny antsonao\\n Nikiry biby aho,nanao ny tsy sitrakao\\n Variana sy sondriana nilalao\\n Ny foko dia nikatona tsy nety nivoha\\n Ninia tsy nampandroso Anao ry Tompo Tsitoha\\n Finaritra loatra ka tsy tsiaro Edena\\n Tsy nataoko an_doha izay famonjena\\n\\n  Refrain:\\n Hifonako tokoa Jeso,hifonako izay vitako\\n Diso aho ka mitalaho\\n Henoy ka aza lavinao\\n Oh ouh oh ouh oh(2*)aza lavinao\\n Hifonako,mifona aho\\n Diso tena diso\\n Hifonako fa diso aho\\n Mifona aho Jesoa tena diso\\n\\n  2)Izao tontolo izao miharendrika koa\\n Misavoritaka sy mifamaky loha\\n Korontana,safotofoto,ranomaso\\n Mitombo ny asa ratsy sy ny ankaso\\n Ny fo sy saina tony mba omeo anay\\n Ny tabataba sy ady,aoka hitsahatra hatreo\\n Ny tonombavakay re ry Tompo mba raiso\\n Ampangino ireo mpanatsatso\\n Mangataka aho ry Tompo mba omeo anay\\n Firaisan_tsaina sy fifankatiavana\\n Ny fiovam_po sy fiainam_baovao\\n Ho santatry ny fiadananay\\n tapitra fin'),
