(104, 'AZA KIVY Raoeliarijao', 'AZA KIVY\\n\\n Raha sendra ka maloka ny andro, manjombona tsisy masoandro,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n Raha tsy tratra izay nokasaina, mba niezaka fa nody maina,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n Raha tonga izay tsy fananana, ka tsy hita izay horaisin\' ny tanana,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n\\n  Raha niendaka izay nifikirana, niady irery ny tena, sahirana,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n Raha misy ny manendrikendrika, mitoraka sady manenjika,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n Raha sendra sakaiza manody, mamitaka tsy mataho-tody,\\n  Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n Raha nihanika lalana avo, voadona ny tena ka lavo, Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n Raha henatra tonga mimpoaka, ka masiaka ny vavam-bahoaka,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n N\'inona n\'inona onjan\' ny fiainana, mamely mandratra fisainana,\\n Aza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\\n tapitra fin'),
(105, 'Miantso anao hatry ny ela Jeso', 'Miantso anao hatry ny ela Jeso\\n Maniry mafy hamonjy anao\\n Henonao foana, fa tsy nahoanao.\\n Dia ny fandavana sy hatak\' andro hatrany no \\nnataonao\\n Mbola tsy androany f\' indray andro any.\\n\\n  Efa impiry moa izy\\n no niangavy anao hanolotena\\n Saingy indrisy tsy nekenao.\\n Ny sarobidy indrindra\\n no natolony ho famonjena.\\n Hatramin\' ny ainy dia nomeny.\\n\\n  Ka mbola inona indray\\n re no azony atao\\n Fa ho anaiky ho vonjeny ianao\\n Tsy misy intsony anie\\n ny mihoatra noho izao;\\n Nefa toa tsy mahataitra anao.\\n Mahonena anie ny safidinao.\\n Saingy tsy terena ve\\n dia manao toy izao. \\n\\n Manoro hevitra anao aho anio\\n Aza mba mangataka andro\\n Ny rahampitso dia tsy fantatrao\\n Anio ianao no nandre\\n izao antsony izao;\\n Manantona dia araraoty\\n Mbola afaka ianao.\\n\\n  Fa maro be tokoa ireo mikasa fa hoe\\n Atsy ho atsy vao hivavaka.\\n Tsy vitsy koa ireo miandry ho efa lehibe\\n Vao hanompo an\'A/tra\\n Mifampiandry, Hay nody mandry.\\n Ny afarany, vovotany.\\n Araraoty izao andro izao\\n Atolory ny tenanao.\\n tapitra fin'),
(106, 'Menatra aho jesosy malala Raoeliarijao', '#MENATRA_AHO_JESOSY_MALALA\\n\\n Mazoto mankany am-piangonana, fa ny fo mbola\\n be fialonana;\\n Isan\'andro mamaky baiboly, fa ny saina mbola\\n an\'ny devoly; Kristiana efa vita batisa, fa mitana ny\\n fanaon\'ny jentilisa;\\n Mitory dia tena mandahatra, fa ny fiainana\\n angaha resy lahatra? Mivavaka manao tsara tafy, fa ny\\n ambadika dia\\n mampirafy;\\n Midera mihira chorale fa mangalatra mamonjy bal;\\n Maha te ho tia fa mpihira, hay olona mpaniratsira;\\n Malaza @ adidy rehetra fa saingy tsy mety miova ny toetra;\\n Jerena toa manan-komena fa ny betsaka fitiavan-tena;\\n Deraina fa tena mpivavaka, fa indrisy mpanavakavaka;\\n Any ivelany maha te ho havana, fa ao atrano tsy misy fitiavana;\\n Androany, ahoana ralahy, rahapitso angaha fantatro ialahy;\\n Nantsoina ho mpiandry ondry, fa mbola mamely totondry;\\n Tsy miandany ambony pilopitra, fa misoko manao politika;\\n Rehefa midera manandratra, rehefa miaingo mitanjaka;\\n Raha sitrapo dia mizihitra, fa rakitra kosa mahihitra;\\n Fanompoana toa tsy misy tasy, hay mbola manao ody gasy;\\n Mba mifady an\'izao sy izatsy, fa mifikitra @fanao ratsy;\\n He!!! kristiana ambony latabatra, fa andrasan\'ny tompo @sabatra;\\n #Mifona_aho_fa_zanaka_adala , #vonjeo_aho_fa_vonon_kiala .\\n tapitra fin'),
