(127, 'Manana Finoana eh!', 'Miandry manantena tsy ho ela ny fiverenanao\\n Aoka samy hanontany tena hoe:vonona ve aho\\n Raha anio ilay fotoana hisehoany\\n Iza re no ho faly sy ho tony\\n Fa tampotampoka,hantomotra sy ankatoka \\n\\n -Averiko foana e\\n Ho avy Jesosy\\n Manana finoana e\\n Ho avy tokoa(diovy ny fo)\\n  Ireo famantarana dia marobe no efa mitranga\\n Gazety,onjam-peo,mampandre mandrangaranga\\n Ny baiboly efa ela no nilaza\\n Ny zavatra rehetra efa mazava\\n Ka azo antoka fa hantomotra sy hankatoka\\n\\n  Dieny mbola misy ny fotoana dia tapaho ny hevitrao\\n Aoka koa tsy hinohino foana hoe zao na izao\\n Zay voalaza sy voasoratra ihany\\n No hinoana sy ekena hatrany\\n Aza mafy hatoka,fa Jeso ho avy tampoka.\\n tapitra fin'),
(128, '#DIOVY_AHO Ambatomanga', '#DIOVY_AHO\\n\\n Eo ampelatananao tokoa no apetrako izao\\n ny fiainako ry Raiko na tsy mendrika ho Anao\\n Efa fantatrao ny amiko tsy miafina Aminao\\n Na mipetraka dia hitanao na mitsangana ihany koa\\n\\n Ref:\\n Diovy aho sasao madio ho mendrika Anao .Oh\\n miangavy Anao\\n Tantano re ka mba Ianao\\n No antompianako ety\\n Diovy aho sasao madio\\n Ho mendrika Anao \\n Oh miangavy Anao\\n Tantano re ka mba Ianao\\n No antompiainako ety\\n\\n Ny talentako fiteniko ny fijery ihany koa\\n Raiso izy ireo tantano\\n Mba hitera bokatsoa\\n Miangavy Anao ry Raiko o\\n Mitoetra ato ampo \\n Aza avelanao ho irery aho\\n Mba ho zanakao doria\\n\\n Ref:\\n <b> AMBATOMANGA\\n tapitra fin'),
(129, '#HARENAKO LOVA MIAMPITA', '#HARENAKO\\n\\n 1) Tsy ho azonao antsaina ny hafaliana anatiko ao\\n Satria tsy mba ivelany ihany toy ny anizao tontolo\\n izao \\n Fa hafaliana avy ao anaty miorina tsy mety maty\\n Ambony ny finoko an\'i Jeso\\n Na hesorina amiko aza izay rehetra ananako\\n Raha mbola velona aho izay ny ahy no tanako\\n Harenako Jesosy tia fananako doria doria tsy misy\\n atakaloko azy sanatria\\n\\n  2) Hanontany angamba ia nao hoe fa dia nahoana \\nindrindra re \\n Dia tsotra ihany no lazaiko ho valin izany teninao\\n Ny heloko dia nofafany ny gadrako dia novahany\\n Ny fiainako dia nohavaoziny\\n Ilay fiadanampony no indro fa nomeny ahy \\n Ary ny famimdrampony no injao mameno ny fanahy\\n Tsy misy raha ny toizao ny zavatra efa itanao\\n Tena ambony ny fitiavan Jeso \\n\\n 3) Fanandramana ilaina hampitombona herimpo \\n Zay tsapa fa miha mirona latsaka ambany tokoa \\n Mila miarina raha lavo miankina amin\' Ilay Avo\\n Nanaiky ho faty tany Kalvary\\n Tsy ampy hery handresena ny ratsy nahazatra anao\\n Fa Jesosy famonjena no antoka hanampy anao\\n Dia eo ianao no miantoraha\\n Teo aho no nanao fampitaha \\n Ny fitiavany tsy miova ho doria \\n\\n  LOVA MIAMPITA\\n tapitra fin'),
(130, '***SOA IHANY***(Njato sy Tafika)', '***SOA IHANY***\\n\\n (Njato sy Tafika)\\n ==========\\n Soa ihany aho Jeso teo anilanao\\n Raha niharan\'izao fitsapana izao\\n Fa raha ts\'izany angamba dia loza izay nanjo\\n Fa tena very hevitra aho\\n Soa teo anilako ianao ho tokiko re\\n\\n  Soa ihany aho Jeso nampahoriana\\n Hianarako ireo zay fitsipikao\\n Hampahendry ahy mihoatra noho ireo fahavaloko\\n Satria ato anatiko sy efa ivelomako\\n Ireo didinao ho mandrakizay\\n\\n  Ref: F\'ao aminao dia ho maivana daholo ireo fakam-panahy\\n Satria ianao no nitondra sy nilanja ireo \\nmavesatray\\n Sady mahatoky sy marina,mamela ireo helokay\\n Tomoera Tompo Ã´ aty anatinay\\n Ianao\\n (annnnn)\\n\\n  Soa ihany aho Jeso nampahoriana\\n Hianarako ireo zay fitsipikao\\n Hampahendry ahy mihoatra noho ireo fahavaloko\\n Satria ato anatiko sy efa hivelomako\\n Ireo didinao ho mandrakizay\\n\\n  Ref: F\'ao aminao dia ho maivana daholo...\\n Toa nofafanao ty fahadisoanay\\n Nodiovinao t@ ny ranao soa\\n\\n  Ref: F\'ao aminao dia ho maivana daholo...\\n tapitra fin'),
(131, 'Faniriako Ray Ã´ ROHAMA', ':;:Faniriako Ray Ã´\\n\\n  Ny ho eo ankaikinao\\n Anilanao mandrakizay\\n Arovy aho\\n Tantano fa sao mania\\n Ny herinao no tokiko:;:\\n Aza manahy fa tsy ho irery ianao\\n Ho anilanao mandrakizay\\n\\n  Hiaro anao hitantana anao koa \\n (Lehilahy)ny heriko ho tokinao\\n (Vehivavy)ny herinao ho tokiko\\n Na sarotra izay aleha\\n (Lehilahy)ny tanako ho tokinao\\n Vehivavy)ny tananao no tokiko\\n Azoniko ka tsy avelako\\n (Lehilahy)ny sandriko hiaro anao\\n (vehivavy)ny sandrinao hiaro ahy\\n Faniriako ray o....\\n Aza manahy...\\n\\n  Ref\\n Tsy ho irery aho fa\\n Ho eo anilanao\\n Hiaro anao ho tokinao\\n Tsy hisaraka aminao\\n N\'aiza aleha \\n Ianao no malalako\\n Ref.na sarotr\'izay aleha...\\n Azoniko ka tsy avelako\\n Ianao no malalako\\n\\n Mpihira:Rohama\\n tapitra fin'),
(132, '~~~Masoandro~~~ Efitra', '~~~Masoandro~~~\\n\\n Io lay masoandro mitondra azavana\\n Sy tara-pitiavana koa\\n Io lay masoandro mitondra hafanana\\n Manaitra anao mba hifoha\\n Mizara ny soa sy tsara\\n Hitory sy hanambara\\n Hanao zay azo atao\\n Toetra miavaka tsy manavakavaka\\n Na inona toeranao\\n\\n  Io lay masoandro raha hilentika koa\\n Dia mbola mampanantena\\n Fa rahampitso hivimbina zavatsoa\\n Ny bitsik\'ilay taratra mena\\n Hizara ny soa sy tsara\\n Hitory sy hanambara\\n Hanao zay azo atao\\n Toetra miavaka tsy manavakavaka\\n Na inona toeranao\\n\\n  Na takona semban-drahona aza\\n Dia mibaliaka kosa any ambony\\n Mamiko loatra tiako ny milaza\\n Tsy hoe zay dia tsy hipoitra intsony\\n F\'Hizara ny soa sy tsara\\n Hitory sy hanambara\\n Hanao zay azo atao\\n Toetra miavaka tsy manavakavaka\\n Na inona toeranao\\n\\n Efitra\\n tapitra fin'),
(133, 'Ny fanantenako  Choral Feon\' ny Fanantenana Ambohijafy. Adventiste Ambohijafy Eglise', 'Ny fanantenako\\n\\n  1) Ny faratampon\' ny fanantenako dia izao,\\n Ny ahita maso lay mpanavotra ahy sy ianao.\\n Ny faratampon\' ny fifaliako dia izao.\\n Ny ahita maso lay tia ahy sy ianao.\\n\\n  2) Rehefa hoavy tsy hoela,Eny andrahondanitra.\\n Jesosy Tompo lay mpanavotra ahy sy ianao.\\n Ny fahoriana,fijaliana,\\n Amin\' izay ho tapitra,\\n Sambatra isika ao an danitra.\\n\\n  ( ref) Ho hitako tokoa re,\\n Amin\' izay fotoana izay.\\n Ny tavan\' i Jehovah Ray.\\n Ho hitako tokoa re,\\n Amin\' izay fotoana izay.\\n Jesosy fitiavana.\\n\\n  3) Tsy hisy intsony ranomaso na fahafatesana.\\n Tsy hisy fangirifiriana na fanaintanana.\\n Fa efa Lasa avokoa,ireo zavatra taloha.\\n Hisolo paradisa tena soa. \\n\\n ( ref) Ho hitantsika rehetra izao.\\n Amin\' izay fotoana izay.\\n Ny tavan\' i Jehovah Ray.\\n Ho hitantsika rehetra izao.\\n Amin\' izay fotoana izay.\\n Jesosy fitiavana.\\n\\n  Choral Feon\' ny Fanantenana Ambohijafy. Adventiste\\n Ambohijafy Eglise\\n tapitra fin'),
(134, 'Amorony fo madio aho Amorony fo vaovao HANITR\'I KRISTY', 'Amorony fo madio aho\\n Amorony fo vaovao\\n\\n  1)O!Amorony fo vaovao aho\\n Fo vaovao tahaka ny Anao \\n Iriko indrindra Ray ny ho tahaka Anao\\n O!Amorony fo vaovao\\n\\n  Refrain:\\n \'Reo toetrako taloha\\n Homboiko avokoa\\n Ambony hazo fijalianao ry Jeso Mpamonjy o!\\n O!Mba ampio aho\\n Ka mba tohano fa tsy hefako irery \\n Izao faniriako izao\\n\\n  2)\'Reo lalandratsiko mahazatra ahy\\n \'Reo fomba ratsy izay niainako\\n Tsy hiverenako,efa neniko tokoa\\n O!Amorony fo vaovao\\n\\n  Refrain:....\\n Amorony fo madio aho\\n Amorony fo vaovao\\n\\n HANITR\'I KRISTY\\n tapitra fin'),
(135, 'RY JESO ZOKY GROUPE LALAO', 'RY JESO ZOKY\\n\\n  1)Ry Jeso Zoky o!\\n Taminao no nahavonjy anay\\n Fa efa latsaka tao anaty haizina\\n Ry Jeso Zoky o!\\n Maminay ny Anaranao\\n Manadio anay mpanota Ianao\\n Jeso fitiavana\\n\\n  2)Ry Jeso Zoky o!\\n Sitrakay ny hanome Anao\\n Ity fonay manontolo\\n Eny raiso ho tranonao\\n Ny andronay Jeso\\n Ho Anao mandrakizay\\n Manadio anay mpanota Ianao\\n Jeso fitiavana\\n Ny ratra nentinao\\n Sy ny latsa niharetanao\\n Namela holatra\\n Mampiseho fitiavana\\n Ry Jeso Zoky o!\\n Tianay,malalanay\\n (Manadio ny ota vitanay\\n Ianao,Jesosy o!)*2\\n\\n GROUPE LALAO\\n tapitra fin'),
(136, '\'ZAHO HIANDRY ANAO Hanitri\'Kristy', '\'ZAHO HIANDRY ANAO\\n\\n  1)Moa ny tany ve?No voahozona\\n Tsy hisy zava_mahasoa\\n F\'izay rehetra mba alehanao\\n Toa fitaka avokoa\\n Fa torovana sady reraka\\n Izany saina sy ny fo\\n Toa satriko hikopak\'elatrToa satriko \\nhikopak\'elatra\\n Nefa mba ho aiza moa\\n\\n  Ref:\\n Fa miandry sy matoky ny fiverenanao\\n Tompo o!Na sarotra ny dia\\n Manantena ilay tany sy lanitra vaovao\\n Na dia mafy aza ny ady ety\\n Tompo o!\'Zaho hiandryTompo o!\'Zaho hiandry Anao\\n O!Ampio tsy ho potraka\\n Eny fa na haharitra\\n \'Zaho hiandry Anao\\n\\n  2)Raha ny heriko\\n Dia tsy afaka hisedra zava_tsarotra\\n Mangataka ny fanohananao\\n Mba tsy ho kivy aho\\n Fa tsy manana ianteherana\\n Afa_tsy ilay sandrinao\\n Ny hany mba italahoako\\n Ampaherezo aho\\n tapitra fin'),
(137, '~~~~~MPITANTANA~~~~~ Balsama', 'MPITANTANA\\n\\n  Iza moa no olona ety an-tany\\n No mahay mamantatra n\'a maminany\\n Zay rehetra tsara sy ilainy\\n Jamba aho Tompo Ã´ ka mila hatrany\\n  Mpitantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro isan\'andro\\n Mpanafaka amin\'ny olana s\'y izay mety mahazo\\n Fa Ianao,Ianao Jeso no mahalala\\n Na izay miafina,na tsy ambara\\n Indrandray anie aho misalasala \\n Fa Ianao Jeso,Ianao tsy miala\\n Mitantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro, isanandro\\n Manafaka ny olana sy izay mety mahazo Ianao\\n Ianao Jeso no Hery sy apingako\\n Ka tsy hanan-tahotra aho fa eo Ianao\\n  Mitantantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro isanandro\\n Manafaka n\'y olana s\'y izay mety mahazo\\n Mitantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro isan\'andro\\n Ka dia misaotra anao satria Ianao efa ampy ho Ahy\\n Fa Ianao,Jeso Ianao tsy miala\\n\\n  Balsama\\n tapitra fin'),
(138, 'Sabata Jacqueline', 'Andro iray nomen\'i TOMPO\\n Andro tokana tsy miova\\n Nohamasininy.\\n Notahiany tena miavaka\\n Mba ho famantarana AZY\\n Ilay Mpamorona,\\n Dia nomeny ahy sy ianao\\n Mba ho fitsaharana,\\n Ary mbola hitoetra\\n Eny! Ho mandrakizay.\\n\\n  IZY mihintsy no niteny \\n Nanao Sonia.\\n Io no famantarana Amiko sy hianao\\n Mbola ho tsarovana\\n Eny! Na any an-danitra\\n NY SABATA fitsaharana,\\n Tsy miova fa maharitra.\\n\\n  Groupe Jacqueline\\n tapitra fin'),
