(152, '~~~Feno tahotra~~~', '~~~Feno tahotra~~~\\n\\n ;:; Feno tahotra,NY fiainako\\n Feno takona zay rehetra alehako\\n Feno toky re misy hery vao\\n Raha Jeso anilanao :;:\\n\\n RÃ©f:\\nTsy misy hery hianteherana raha misaraka aminao\\n Eo anilanao no fanamperana\\n Lay sakaizako tsy mba mandao\\n Sambatra aho re Jeso tokiko\\n Izy miantoka NY anio sy ny hoaviko\\n Ny fanahiana be esoriny avokoa\\n Ka tolorany reo mahasoa\\n Ref:(2*)\\n Eo anilanao (2*)\\n\\n Rohama\\n  ******************************************************************'),
(153, 'Tompo Ã´ omeo hery aho', 'Tompo Ã´ omeo hery aho\\n\\n  Mba hanompoko anao\\n Sy hanandratako ny voninahitrao\\n Omeo saina koa\\n Mba handinika ny fiainako\\n Na be izany na madinika\\n\\n  Ref:\\n Aiza moa Ianao ry Mpamonjiko\\n Fa ny fiainako lavitra anao\\n Ka ninoninona atao\\n Dia aoka mba ho voninahitrao\\n Ny angatahiko,ny angatahiko\\n Ankasitrahanao ry Ray Tsitoha\\n\\n   Tompo Ã´ omeo hery aho\\n Mba hiderako anao\\n Sy Tanjaka koa mba hiantsoako anao\\n Sarotra tokoa ny ho diavinay\\n Ianao no ilainay \\n Hiara-dalana tsy afoy anay\\n Ref:aiza moa.....\\n\\n Hasina\'s Groupe\\n  *****************'),
(154, 'Manankarena Fitiavana Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa', 'Manankarena Fitiavana Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa ClÃ©: Sol\\n\\n 1.\\n Ny hasasarako ho maivana fa entinao ny entako \\n Ny hetaheta ho afaka Ianao no loharano soa\\n Manankarena fitiavana Ianao fahasoavana be\\n Tsy misy izay tsy anananao , Anao zao rehetr\'izao\\n Ref:\\n Sambatra aho fa zanakao ,Eny malalanao\\n Izaho sy Ianao no hiaradia hifampitantan\'ho doria\\n Hatrety ka hatrany an -danitra ,hiaraka \\nmandrakizay\\n 2.\\n Ny adin - tsaina zay mandreraka , soloina fiadanam - po\\n Ny fahoriana zay mahasasatra , ho tonga fifaliana\\n Manankarena fitiavana Ianao fahasoavana be\\n Tsy misy izay tsy anananao , Anao zao rehetr\'izao\\n\\n Ref:\\n\\n  3.\\n Entiko eo aminao avoko, reo zava - tsarotra manjo\\n Mahatoky ny fitanananao, Ianao \'lay Tompo tsy \\nmandao\\n Manankarena fitiavana Ianao fahasoavana be\\n Tsy misy izay tsy anananao , Anao zao rehetr\'izao\\n\\n Ref:\\n  (Miakatra clÃ© La)\\n Ref:\\n Sambatra aho fa zanakao ,Eny malalanao\\n Izaho sy Ianao no hiaradia hifampitantan\'ho doria\\n Hatrety ka hatrany an -danitra ,hiaraka mandrakizay\\n mandrakizay ( miadana)\\n ******************************'),
(155, 'Ilay feo - Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa', 'Ilay feo - Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa\\n\\n 1.\\n Ao an-tsofinao ao sy ny eritreritrao\\n Misy bitsika hoe :\"lÃ lan\'aiza no aleha?\"\\n Lala - migodana ve izay betsaka mpandeha\\n Tsisy sakan - dÃ lana nefa tsisy hifandrarÃ na\\n Miangavy anao diniho \'zay atao\\n Fa hoy ny teny :\" na maro ireny, \\n dia tsy voatery ho any amin\'ireny,\\n no mahavonjy ny ainao!\"\\n\\n Ref:\\n Mba henoy ilay feo iray,\\n Mitondra anao ho amin - dRay!\\n\\n 2.\\n Toa tamin\'ny andron\'i Noa valo mianaka\\n Maro izay nifidy hoe:\\n \"maro anisa hatrany hatrany\"\\n Kanjo dia nanenina, ranomaso ozona \\n Zary fahafatesana , no niandry azy ireo\\n Koa jereo tsara , f\'ilay anjara\\n  Dia ny safidy atao anio \\n Tsy miankina aminy ny olotianao\\n  Na koa ny ray sy reninao\\n\\n Ref:\\n Mba henoy ilay feo iray,\\n Mitondra anao ho amin - dRay!\\n Mitondra anao ho amin - dRay!\\n\\n Misy feo tsy manery \\n Mora nefa azo antoka \\n Raha zatra nandÃ  ianao \\n Dia tsy re intsony ilay feo! \\n O! O!!!!!! O!!!! \\n Ilay feo!\\n ********************'),
(156, 'Anatra Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa', 'Anatra Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa\\n\\n 1.(duo unisson)\\n Ry zanakay malala oh, tinay tena tinay\\n Izao no mba irinay , tena fifalianay\\n Tianay raha ianao hotafita rahatrizay!\\n\\n Ref:\\n (vehivavy)\\n Dada oh! ry neniko malala!\\n Ianareo no andry hiankinanay\\n (trio voix 1,2,3)\\n\\n Raha tsy ianareo ho iza moa no hampianatra \\n Raha tsy ianao ho iza koa no hananatra\\n Koa fisaorana no atolotray , Misaotra eh!\\n\\n 2.(duo unisson)\\n Ny hanovo fahendrena, Zany no katsaho\\n Fa ny fahadalana ,\' zany ialao\\n Fahalalana tadiavo, dia ho sambatra\\n (duo)\\n Ianao\\n\\n Ref: \\n (vehivavy)\\n Dada oh! ry neniko malala!\\n Ianareo no andry hiankinanay\\n (trio voix 1,2,3)\\n Raha tsy ianareo ho iza moa no hampianatra\\n  Raha tsy ianao ho iza koa no hananatra\\n Koa fisaorana no atolotray , Misaotra eh!\\n (trio voix 1,2,3)\\n Dada oh! ry neniko malala!\\n Ianareo no andry hiankinanay\\n Raha tsy ianareo ho iza moa no hampianatra \\n Raha tsy ianao ho iza koa no hananatra\\n Koa fisaorana no atolotray , Misaotra eh!\\n Koa fisaorana no atolotray , Misaotra eh!\\n (unisson)\\n Fisaorana no a ..\\n (trio voix 1,2,3)\\n .tolotray\\n ***********************'),
(157, 'Hiova aho', 'Hiova aho Billy \\n\\n  Tolory hery sy finoana aho Ray,\\n  ahaizako manao. Ireo rehetra izay,\\n  tsy nety hatramin\'izay tsy sitrao.\\n  Ankehitriny izao, vao tsapako fa hay ny\\n  fahendrenao ihany no tokony hokatsahiko. \\n Ray Ã´! ampianaro aho, izay tena sitrakao.\\n  Mba ho olom-baovao, ho mendrika ho Anao.\\n  Ka tsy hiverin-dalana intsony satria,\\n  efa nametraka ilay voady hoe: \\n \\n  \"Hiova aho, hanaraka ny sitrakao. \\n Hiova aho, ho hamasino \\n  tsy hania intsony hoe: hiova aho, \\n f\'izay no fanantenako hatrizay. \\n Ka hotanako fa tsara, hoan\'ny fiainako\"\\n\\n   Sasao madio aho Ray, \\n mba hiova ka hanara-dia Anao. \\n Hahay hitondra ireo talenta, \\n ho entina mba hiderana Anao.\\n  Hifonako eto anio, \\n ireo ota vitako hatrizay.\\n  Ny famelanao ihany,\\n  no hahafan-keloka ahy.\\n**************************************');
