(55, '~~Aza kivy,aza ketraka~~', '~~Aza kivy,aza ketraka~~\r\n\r\nRaha sendra midona n\'y oram-baratra\r\nKay maizina rÃ©,ny lalana aleha\r\nTsy hita intsony zay amaharana\r\nO miandrandra ka jereo fa ao Jeso\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nAza kivy,ooooo\r\nAza ketraka f\'izay ny lalana\r\nEfa nalehan\'i Jeso\r\nAza kivy oooo\r\nAza ketraka\r\nF\'izay ny lalana efa nalehany\r\n\r\nRaha toa ny anjara masoandronao\r\nNo semban-drahona\r\nJeso no masoandro izay tsy mety takona\r\nRaha toa ka tsy hitanao irony kintana\r\nJeso miara-mita hitantana anao\r\nRÃ©f:aza kivy....(2*)'),
(56, 'Tsy manavakavaka', 'Tsy manavakavaka\r\nizay manana fitiavana\r\nFa ilay fihavanana\r\nno hery mampikambana\r\n\r\nka na samihafa aza re ireo fihaviana\r\nIza ary no mandÃ \r\nfa tsy iray fianakaviana.\r\nIlana vahaolana\r\n\r\nilay fahavalo iray hiombonana\r\nTsy izay fihodirana\r\nfa izay mety ho fifandirana\r\nMitovy isika olom_belona\r\ntaranak\' i Adama\r\nIza ary no mandÃ \r\nfa tsy mila fanafahana.\r\n\r\nAny andro any taona,\r\nity tany fandalovana\r\nAdilahy nampivoana\r\ntsy misy hotsarovana\r\nka ho anareo ary ho anay\r\nilay tanana masina\r\nireo izay mety mifandray\r\nho tonga zanaky ny Ray.'),
(57, 'Izaho Jesosy mba maniry', 'Izaho Jesosy mba maniry\r\nny anao ny sitrakao;\r\nEfa ela no nikiry,\r\ntsy nahomby hatramin\' izao.\r\nRaha anio mandre ny antsonao\r\ndia torotoro fo;\r\nToa hiova olom-baovao,\r\ntapakevitra hifoa.\r\n\r\nNefa izany tsy maharitra,\r\ntsy mba mety ho lasa lavitra;\r\nRahampitso dia injay\r\nny omaliko no miverina indray.\r\nIzaho Jesosy mba tantano\r\nO! Arovy sy tohano;\r\nMiangavy mitoreo!!\r\nJesosy o vonjeo,\r\nIty zandrinao vonjeo.\r\n\r\nToriteny maro no efa re,\r\nbe ny anatra voaray;\r\nFa ny hampiatr\' ireny anie\r\ndia toa sarotra tsy hay.\r\nVao mandroso indray mandingana\r\nhoe hanaraka anao\r\ndia indro fa voafingana,\r\npotraka sy lavo aho.\r\n\r\nTsy azo antoka ny hoaviko;\r\nTsisy antenaina ny amiko.\r\nRaha tsy tantananao\r\ndia inoko fa tsy ho tafita aho.\r\nAza avela andeha irery\r\nO! Ampio fa kely hery\r\nMiangavy mitoreo!!\r\nJesosy o vonjeo,\r\nIty zandrinao vonjeo'),
(58, 'IZAHO DIA ZANAKAO GROUPE SAMBATRA', 'IZAHO DIA ZANAKAO\r\n\r\nHiezaka aho ny hanamafy\r\nNy finoako Anao ry Ray\r\nKa na ho mora na ho mafy\r\nFa izaho dia zanakao\r\nVonona aho ny hijoro\r\nHisaina mafy izay efa azoko\r\nKoa ny misy horohoro\r\nNy Paradisa efa tazako\r\n\r\nNy hiemotra dia sanatria \r\nVita dina,vita voady ny aty\r\nKa izay hanao hoe tsia \r\nDia ataoko ho tena fady \r\n\'Reo ny ahy no tanjoko\r\nTsy avelako hisy ho foana\r\nKoa izay mety fara androko\r\nNy hanamafy ny finoana\r\n\r\n(Finoako Anao Ray)2 fois\r\nHiezaka aho ny hanamafy\r\n(Ny finoako Anao ry Ray)2 fois\r\nKa na ho mora na ho mafy\r\n(Fa izaho dia zanakao)2 fois\r\nHiezaka aho ny hanamafy......\r\n\r\nGROUPE SAMBATRA'),
(59, '***Ny Hatanorana***', '***Ny Hatanorana***\r\nAndro soa sady kanto izany hatanorana\r\nToy ny raozy vao maraina,tsara famelana\r\nEo ny hatsaran-tarehy,endrika sy bika soa\r\nIzay mambabo fo tokoa tena mamy\r\nEo koa no mitsiry ny fitia\r\nAndro hafa tena hafa eo amin\'ny fiainana\r\nKa hiriany izany mba haharitra\r\n\r\nAndron\'ny korana,androm-pifaliana\r\nHandresena hakiviana\r\nHanovozan-kery,hamakin\'onja mahery\r\nAntoky ny any aoriana\r\n\r\nMarobe ny fitsapana,misedra ny hatanorana\r\nAo ireo filibana,fisotroana,filokana\r\nFitondran-tena tsy hendry mety hamarina\r\nKa handratra sy hampamoy fo\r\nToe-panahy sy fisainana madio\r\nNo hitondra hasambarana sy voninahitra\r\nToetra soa,tsara ho filamatra\r\n\r\n'),
(60, 'Dada o ry dada', 'Dada o ry dada\r\nE faly mikotaba\r\nIreto.zanakao\r\nManolotra arahaba\r\nE fetinao.androany\r\nManerana ny tany\r\nKoa raiso re ry dada o\r\nFitia miredareda\r\n\r\nTsy ny kapokapoka\r\nSy trerona ry dada \r\nNo tsy hitiavanay anao\r\nF\'i neny dia sahaza\r\nFitiavanao ireny\r\nNierana tam i neny\r\nKoa raiso re ry dada o\r\nFitia miredareda'),
(61, 'Ilay feo - Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa', 'Ilay feo - Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa\r\n\r\n1.\r\nAo an-tsofinao ao sy ny eritreritrao\r\nMisy bitsika hoe :\"lÃ lan\'aiza no aleha?\"\r\nLala - migodana ve izay betsaka mpandeha\r\nTsisy sakan - dÃ lana nefa tsisy hifandrarÃ na\r\nMiangavy anao diniho \'zay atao\r\nFa hoy ny teny :\" na maro ireny, \r\ndia tsy voatery ho any amin\'ireny,\r\nno mahavonjy ny ainao!\"\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nMba henoy ilay feo iray,\r\nMitondra anao ho amin - dRay!\r\n\r\n2.\r\nToa tamin\'ny andron\'i Noa valo mianaka\r\nMaro izay nifidy hoe:\r\n\"maro anisa hatrany hatrany\"\r\nKanjo dia nanenina, ranomaso ozona \r\nZary fahafatesana , no niandry azy ireo\r\nKoa jereo tsara , f\'ilay anjara \r\nDia ny safidy atao anio \r\nTsy miankina aminy ny olotianao \r\nNa koa ny ray sy reninao\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nMba henoy ilay feo iray,\r\nMitondra anao ho amin - dRay!\r\nMitondra anao ho amin - dRay!\r\n\r\nMisy feo tsy manery \r\nMora nefa azo antoka \r\nRaha zatra nandÃ  ianao \r\nDia tsy re intsony ilay feo! \r\nO! O!!!!!! O!!!! \r\nIlay feo!'),
(62, 'AZA KIVY Raoeliarijao', 'AZA KIVY\r\nRaha sendra ka maloka ny andro, manjombona tsisy masoandro,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nRaha tsy tratra izay nokasaina, mba niezaka fa nody maina,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nRaha tonga izay tsy fananana, ka tsy hita izay horaisin\' ny tanana,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\n\r\nRaha niendaka izay nifikirana, niady irery ny tena, sahirana,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nRaha misy ny manendrikendrika, mitoraka sady manenjika,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nRaha sendra sakaiza manody, mamitaka tsy mataho-tody,\r\n\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nRaha nihanika lalana avo, voadona ny tena ka lavo,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nRaha henatra tonga mimpoaka, ka masiaka ny vavam-bahoaka,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.\r\nN\'inona n\'inona onjan\' ny fiainana, mamely mandratra fisainana,\r\nAza kivy fa mandalo izany, fa ny fiainana tsy androany ihany.'),
(63, 'Miantso anao hatry ny ela Jeso', 'Miantso anao hatry ny ela Jeso\r\nManiry mafy hamonjy anao\r\nHenonao foana, fa tsy nahoanao.\r\nDia ny fandavana sy hatak\' andro hatrany no nataonao\r\nMbola tsy androany f\' indray andro any.\r\n\r\nEfa impiry moa izy\r\nno niangavy anao hanolotena\r\nSaingy indrisy tsy nekenao.\r\nNy sarobidy indrindra\r\nno natolony ho famonjena.\r\nHatramin\' ny ainy dia nomeny.\r\n\r\nKa mbola inona indray\r\nre no azony atao\r\nFa ho anaiky ho vonjeny ianao\r\nTsy misy intsony anie\r\nny mihoatra noho izao;\r\nNefa toa tsy mahataitra anao.\r\nMahonena anie ny safidinao.\r\nSaingy tsy terena ve\r\ndia manao toy izao.\r\n\r\nManoro hevitra anao aho anio\r\nAza mba mangataka andro\r\nNy rahampitso dia tsy fantatrao\r\nAnio ianao no nandre\r\nizao antsony izao;\r\nManantona dia araraoty\r\nMbola afaka ianao.\r\n\r\nFa maro be tokoa ireo mikasa fa hoe\r\nAtsy ho atsy vao hivavaka.\r\nTsy vitsy koa ireo miandry ho efa lehibe\r\nVao hanompo an\'A/tra\r\nMifampiandry, Hay nody mandry.\r\nNy afarany, vovotany.\r\nAraraoty izao andro izao\r\nAtolory ny tenanao.'),
(64, 'Menatra aho jesosy malala Raoeliarijao', '#MENATRA_AHO_JESOSY_MALALA Mazoto mankany am-piangonana, fa ny fo\r\nmbola\r\nbe fialonana;\r\nIsan\'andro mamaky baiboly, fa ny saina\r\nmbola\r\nan\'ny devoly; Kristiana efa vita batisa, fa mitana ny\r\nfanaon\'ny\r\njentilisa;\r\nMitory dia tena mandahatra, fa ny\r\nfiainana\r\nangaha resy lahatra? Mivavaka manao tsara tafy, fa ny\r\nambadika dia\r\nmampirafy;\r\nMidera mihira chorale fa mangalatra\r\nmamonjy\r\nbal; Maha te ho tia fa mpihira, hay olona\r\nmpaniratsira;\r\nMalaza @ adidy rehetra fa saingy tsy\r\nmety miova\r\nny toetra;\r\nJerena toa manan-komena fa ny betsaka fitiavan-tena;\r\nDeraina fa tena mpivavaka, fa indrisy\r\nmpanavakavaka;\r\nAny ivelany maha te ho havana, fa ao\r\natrano tsy\r\nmisy fitiavana; Androany, ahoana ralahy, rahapitso\r\nangaha\r\nfantatro ialahy;\r\nNantsoina ho mpiandry ondry, fa mbola\r\nmamely\r\ntotondry; Tsy miandany ambony pilopitra, fa\r\nmisoko manao\r\npolitika;\r\nRehefa midera manandratra, rehefa\r\nmiaingo\r\nmitanjaka; Raha sitrapo dia mizihitra, fa rakitra kosa\r\nmahihitra;\r\nFanompoana toa tsy misy tasy, hay\r\nmbola\r\nmanao ody gasy;\r\nMba mifady an\'izao sy izatsy, fa mifikitra @fanao ratsy;\r\nHe!!! kristiana ambony latabatra, fa\r\nandrasan\'ny\r\ntompo @sabatra; #Mifona_aho_fa_zanaka_adala , #vonjeo_aho_fa_vonon_kiala .'),
(65, 'Falifaly re ry dada o', '~~~Dada 2005~~~\r\n;:;Falifaly re ry dada o\r\nTena faly miarahaba\r\nFa ny fetinao androany ihany no nandrasanay hatrany;:;\r\n\r\nRef:(Fety mamy)\r\nFety mamy tena mamy\r\n(Ã” mamy)\r\nMety ho feno vatomamy\r\n(Ny mamy)\r\nKa ny tsiky sy tomany\r\nMifamadibadika ambony sy ambany\r\n(Ã”... )\r\n\r\nFalifaly re ry dada o\r\nTena faly miarahaba\r\nFa ny fetinao androany ihany no nandrasanay hatrany\r\n\r\n;:;Falifaly re ry dada o\r\nTena faly mikotaba\r\nFa izany fetinao izany no\r\nNandrasanay androany;:;\r\n\r\nRef:+\r\n\r\nFalifaly re ry dada Ã´ \r\nTena faly mikotaba\r\nFa izany fetinao izany no\r\nNandrasanay androany'),
(66, '~~~Dada~~~', '\r\n~~~Dada~~~\r\nDada Ã´ dada Ã´\r\nTiako ianao\r\nNiafy mafy\r\nnamelona ahy\r\n\r\nRef:Ataoko ahoana no hanadino\r\nO sanatria tsaroako foana\r\nDada o dada o\r\nTsy foiko ianao\r\nNilofo loatra\r\nNahatoy izao ahy\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nDada o dada o\r\nInona kosa\r\nNo avaliko anao\r\nFitia miavosa\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nDada o dada o\r\nMisaotra anao\r\nTi foko kely \r\nAnatiko ao\r\n\r\nRef\r\nHitahy anao anie Jeso\r\nCandy'),
(67, 'Dada', '~~~Dada~~~\r\nAsa raha toa ahalaza ny ao ampoko\r\nZay mankasitraka dada ireo nataonao\r\nIty hira ity izay ho kaloiko indrindra\r\nHo fisaorako anao\r\nSy hilazako tsotra izao\r\nDada tiako ianao\r\n\r\nIanao nanoro ahy ny lalana tsara\r\nSy mikatsaka zay mety ahasoa ahy\r\nTsy notsitsinao ny kapoka famaizana\r\nIreny no nahatoy izao ahy\r\n\r\nAsa raha toa ahalaza ny ao ampoko\r\nZay mankasitraka dada ireo nataonao\r\nIty hira ity izay noforoniko indrindra\r\nHo fisaorako anao sy hilazako tsotra izao\r\nDada tiako ianao\r\n\r\nIanao mitantana ny tanako hatrizay\r\nIsanandro ianao mivavaka ho ahy\r\nSy mametraka ny amiko eo an-tanan\'ilay Ray\r\nIreny no nahatoy izao ahy\r\n\r\n;:;Fisaorana feno\r\nEram-po eran-tsaina\r\nNo atolotro ho anao ry dada be fitia;:;\r\n\r\nSambatra aho,mirehareha a fa zanakao\r\nHisaorako Andriamanitra nanome ahy ianao\r\nFa sambatra aho,mirehareha\r\nFa zanakao\r\nHisaorako Andriamanitra nanome ahy anao\r\nEnganie handova lanitra\r\nNy ankohonanao\r\n\r\nFranca'),
(68, '~~~Dada~~~', '~~~Dada~~~\r\n\r\nDada dada dada\r\nZay mpizara soa\r\nMiasa mafy isan\'andro ianao\r\nTsy aiko ny milaza ny fietseampo\r\nFa ianao tsy mba mahay mandao\r\n\r\nRef:Masoandro,(masoandro)\r\nMamirapiratra ianao(mamirapiratra ianao)\r\nManafana ankohonana\r\nMasoandro(masoandro)\r\nMamirapiratra ianao(mamirapiratra ianao)\r\nZahay sy i neny ko kintana amam-bolana\r\n\r\nDada dada dada\r\nAndry hiankinana\r\nHerin\'ny ankanin-tsika ety\r\nFaly lalandava tsy sahirana\r\nFa Ianao mitarika ny dia\r\n\r\nRef:Masoandro....\r\nDada dada dada\r\nAza ela be raha toa ianao manao tournÃ©â˜º\r\nZa ne mbola zaza neny irery anie\r\nNo eto anilako ka faingana re\r\nMasoandro.....(2*)\r\nZahay sy neny...(3*)\r\nHenitsoa');
