(69, 'Miserana', 'Miserana\r\nFotoana fohy ora vitsy \r\nNo ananao eto an-tany\r\nTehirizo ny tsara izay anananao\r\nMiambena fa tsy fantatrao \r\nZay mety mitranga \r\neo amin\'ny fiainanao\r\nApetrao amin\'i Tompo \r\nAnio ny ho avinao\r\n\r\nRef: Fandalovana ny fiainana\r\nAza atao mahavariana anao\r\nManaova ny tsara \r\nTodio ny any afara\r\nFa toerana soa no miandry anao\r\nFandalovana ny fiainana\r\nMiserana izao rehetra izao\r\nAza sondriana na koa variana \r\nNy Ray no efa miandry ahy sy ianao'),
(70, 'NY TIA SY NY TIANA', 'NY TIA SY NY TIANA\r\n\r\nMifankahita ho azy ny tia sy tiana\r\nRehefa Andriamanitra, manomana fanambadiana\r\nFa Izy no mandahatra ny fiainan\'ny olombelona\r\nIreo izay resy lahatra tsy nahita fanenenana\r\nHinoana fa haharitra\r\nHo tonga hatrany an_danitra\r\n(Hifankahita ho aho ny tia sy ny tiana)x2\r\n\r\nRaha mbola maharitra o ny andron\'ny tany\r\nFifankatiavan\'izy ireo tsy hisy fiafarÃ ny\r\nF\'Ianao no tsy miova omaly sy anio\r\nNy tokantranon\'izy ireo ry Tompo mba tahio\r\nFa tena mahafinaritra ,hinoana fa haharitra \r\n(Hifankahita ho aho ny tia sy ny tiana)x2\r\n\r\nRonono sy tantely izay tany KanÃ na\r\nNo nahatonga ny olona ho lava sy bikÃ na\r\nRaha tenin\' Andriamanitra no ataontsika fihinana\r\nZay tokantranontsika ve tsy ho fenoiny fahamasinana\r\nHinoana fa haharitra, ho tonga hatrany an_danitra\r\nHifankahita ho aho ny tia sy ny tiana\r\n\r\nGROUPE ALISON\r\n'),
(71, 'Teny tsotra', 'Teny tsotra sady fohy \r\nNo hanehoako ny fitiavako\r\nVoninkazo iray fehezana\r\nManitra vao notoazako\r\nIndro atolotro anao Ã´h ry neny mamy\r\nMankasitraka hatrany ireo izay vitanao\r\nTaminay zanakao\r\n\r\nNeny o! Ny voadiko @nao\r\nDia ny ho hendry hanaja anao\r\nFa ny herin\'i Jeso no inoako\r\nFa ho tanterako ireo \r\nÃ”h ry neniko tsy foiko!'),
(72, 'Neny neny', 'Neny neny\r\nTiako tiako\r\nAntsoiko isanandro\r\nNa maraina na atoandro\r\nNeny neny\r\nTiako tiako\r\nNy anaranao no tena mamy ny fo\r\n\r\nVentesiko,hiraiko\r\nIzany hira kanto izany\r\nFa fetinao anie\r\nFotoana lehibe\r\nManandratra ny hatsaranao\r\nHisaoranay Ianao\r\nRy Ray avo indrindra\r\nFa nanome anay\r\nNeny tsara famindra\r\nHo tahinao ny fiainany\r\nHo voninahitrao\r\nNeny neny.....\r\nVentesiko....\r\nNeny neny...'),
(73, '***Amboara ho an\'i Neny***', '***Amboara ho an\'i Neny***\r\nAmboaram-boninkazo\r\nNo atolotro ho anao re ry neny\r\nNo atolotr\'i dada sy ankizy rehetra\r\nSatria fetinao anio\r\nAmboaram-pitiavana\r\nNo atolotr\'ireo zanakao\r\nRy neny nikolo nibaby nitaiza\r\nTsy sasatra nikarakara\r\n\r\nHitahy anao Jeso,hiaro anao izy e\r\nIzany no tonombavakay @ andrompiainanay\r\n\r\nNiaritra ny fahoriana\r\nNigoga ny rano tsy tiana \r\nTsy hoe dokadoka fa hatrany ambohoka d\'efa tia anay ianao\r\nRaha misy marary ampandriana\r\nI neny tsy mba niangaviana\r\nFa tonga matetika andoha-mpandriana\r\nPorofom-pitiavany ahy\r\n\r\nNy vahiny miantrano rehetra\r\nTsy misy tarehy manjoretra\r\nF\'eo ianao ry neny mampifaly ireny porofompitiavana ahy\r\nAo antranon\'ny fianakaviana\r\nMirindra sy feno hafaliana \r\nLapa tsikitsiky tsisy likiliky\r\nSatria manana an\'i neny\r\n\r\nIlay nahary anie tsy hanadino anao\r\nHitantana mandrakizay anao ry neny Ã´\r\nFanaf'),
(74, 'KIBO NIFONOSANA', 'KIBO NIFONOSANA\r\n\r\nKibo nifonosana..\r\n1 .o ry kibo nifonosana,zary dobo nilomanosana\r\nTao aho no nitombo sy niha lehibe\r\nNotahafiko hatramin\'ny bika sy tarehy \r\n..mirana aho no ravo tamin izay\r\nMifaningotra aina tena iray\r\nZay mahasoa ahy no tsy maintsy atao\r\nMihoatra @ fombafomba atao\r\n\r\nVita ihany sivy volana\r\nTonga ny ora hanolorana\r\nNy ainao mihitsy no tena mampanahy\r\nFiry moa no lasana tsy nahy\r\n..koa amin ity ady farany ity\r\nO ampio ry tompo be fitia\r\nTsy fantatro akory ty fahorianao\r\nInona no havaliako izao\r\n\r\nDia nisaotra an Adriamanitra\r\nTody soa isika mianaka\r\nNefa ny asa masinao tsy niato teo\r\nFa nitombo indray teo no eo\r\n...dia nitrotro sy nitantana\r\nNanabe ny tena sy fanahy\r\nNa dia loa jafy aza,tsisy farany\r\nManasoa ireo taranany..\r\n\r\nRef: tsy mba volana iray na roa\r\nNo nitondranao ny mavesatra\r\nAry na maraina vao mifoha\r\nZao foana no ambetindresaka\r\n::::::ity zanako ity anao ahoan moa \r\nIty zanako anao ahoan moa:::;;::'),
(75, 'HO ANâ€™I NENY MALALA TSY FOIKO.', 'HO ANâ€™I NENY MALALA TSY\r\nFOIKO.\r\nHo anâ€™i Neny malala tsy\r\nfoiko\r\nIty tolotra avy aminâ€™ny foko\r\nTonombavaka no omeko\r\nanao\r\n\r\nHo solom-boninkazo fanao\r\nNy Tompo ry Neny malala\r\nNo hitantana tsy hisalasala\r\nHanome ny tsara indrindra\r\nho anao\r\nMihoatra izao fanomezako\r\nizao\r\n\r\nFitiavana sy fahendrena\r\nIreny no azoko omena\r\nHo valim-babena tsy lany\r\nHo anao â€˜lay tokana an-\r\ntany\r\nIty fanomezako kely\r\nToa vitsika momba tantely\r\nNo indro hatolotro anao\r\nNeny Ã´! Tena tiako be\r\nianao.'),
(76, '~~~Neny~~~', '~~~Neny~~~\r\nTena tsapako fa fitiavana \r\nAndriamanitra\r\nNanome ahy ianao\r\nNitondra ahy tao anatinao\r\nNitaiza sy nanolokolo ahy\r\n\r\nRef:Zay nataonao rehetra dia fitia tsy hita fetra\r\nTsy ho voavaliko sanatria\r\nAny heriko hihira\r\nHanambara am-pasahiana\r\nFa hoe tiako tiako ianao\r\n\r\nFola-damosina ianao\r\nNisotro ny rano tsy tiana ianao\r\nNiankin-drindrina irery\r\nTsy nila tambiny velively\r\nTsy nitarai-tana miepaka\r\nFa fitiavana ten fitiavana\r\nNo nanosika anao\r\n\r\nRef:(2*)\r\nKa n\'aiza n\'aiza misy anao\r\nNinononona ataonao\r\nZaho hivavaka ho anao\r\nFa tiako ianao\r\nKa n\'aiza n\'aiza misy anao\r\nNinoninona ataonao\r\nDia tsarovy neny o fa tiako ianao\r\n\r\nFranca'),
(77, '<3 NENY TIA <3', '<3 NENY TIA <3\r\nNeny tia,neny tia\r\nTonga ny fetinao\r\nInona no atolotro ho anao\r\nSanatria,tsy fitia mila dera aminao\r\nNa iangoty mba tiana atao\r\nFa fo te hankasitraka izay vitanao\r\nKa mba te hilaza hoe tsisy toa anao\r\nNeny tia,neny tia\r\nTonga ny fetinao\r\nInona no atolotro ho anao?\r\nSanatria tsy fitia mila dera aminao\r\nNa iangoty mba tiana atao'),
(78, '~~Vavaka ho an\'i neny~~', '~~Vavaka ho an\'i neny~~\r\nRy neny o tsaroako ny fitiavanao\r\nNampianatra nanolokolo anay izao\r\nTadidiko fa niady mafy ianao ry neny\r\nFa raha vady no ianteherana\r\nTsy ela dia efa nody mandry\r\n\r\nNy vavaka mba ho anao ry neny tiana o\r\nAndriamanitra hanampy ny androm-piainanao\r\nHo velona ho tojo zavatra hiriana\r\nKa iara_handova ny fiainana mandrakizay\r\n\r\nAndriamanitra o!tahio ny reninay rehetra\r\nHilami-tsaina re ary ho tena marin-toetra\r\nHavita be ny adidy izay napetrakao\r\nKa ho firenena vanona ny zanaky ny malagasy\r\n\r\nMivavaka ho anareo ry neny tia\r\nAndriamanitra hanampy hery anareo\r\nHo velona ho tojo zavatra hiariana\r\nKa hiara-handova ny fiainana mandrakizay'),
(79, 'AZA MITANONDRI-DAVA_Groupe Harilala', 'AZA MITANONDRI-DAVA_Groupe Harilala\r\nAza mitandondri-dava ry fanahiko\r\nFa banjino lalandava ilay Mpamonjy soa\r\nMatokia ny famonjeny satria Izy no niteny\r\nFa ampy ho anao anie ny fahasoavany\r\nTsy hamela anao irery Jeso be fitia\r\nFa ny masony mijery mitsinjo ny dia\r\nAndrandrao Ilay ao ambony\r\nKa aoka ianao ho tony\r\nFa ampy ho anao anie ny fahasoavany\r\n. . . . . . .\r\nFiverenana:\r\nAza manahy ry foko fa Izy miahy anao\r\nApetraho eo an-tananâ€™ny Tompo ireo tebiteby izay mahazo anao\r\nDia matokia ny famonjeny satria Izy no niteny\r\nFa ampy ho anao anie ny fahasoavany\r\n. . . . . . . \r\n2. misy teny fikasana nomeny anao\r\nManome fanantenana sy hery vaovao\r\nNdeha takio isanâ€™andro raha vao maraina koa ny andro\r\nFa ampy ho anao anie ny fahasoavany\r\nFiverenanaâ€¦â€¦.'),
(80, 'ï»¿AMPAHEREZO (grp Tiaray)', 'ï»¿AMPAHEREZO (grp Tiaray)\r\n1. Be ny olana ety nefa vitsy ny soa\r\nZany foana no iainana ety\r\nNefa tsy ho kivy satria ho afaka\r\nfa Jeso ho avy eny andanitra.\r\nREF \r\nAmpaherezo aho Jeso mba hatoky anao\r\nka hibanjina io lanitra io\r\nho vonona hiaino ilay feonao\r\nzay miantso ahy hoe avia.\r\n2. Reo namako maro dia nandao anao\r\ntsy nandray ny vonjy nomenao\r\nvariana milalao sy miriaria\r\nka manao ny eto ho doria.\r\n3. Manotany tena hoe avy aiza moa\r\nny fahamendrehana ananako\r\nfa Jeso nilaza fa ho avy indray\r\nmba haka ahy ho any @ Ray.'),
(81, 'Ny teninao izay nomena ho anay', 'Ny teninao izay nomena ho anay\r\nManavao mambabo fo fanahy\r\nNy teninao harena soa tsy lany\r\nNatobakao ho lova soa zay mamy\r\nNy teninao fitaratra zay nampianjaka\r\nNy ota niafina tam-po nitanjaka\r\nNy teninao nanafaka sy nanadio indray\r\nNy teninao fanilo soa ho anay\r\nNy teninao nanaitra ilay finoana anatinay\r\nHifaharana aminao.lay izy hatrizay\r\nNandrodana ireo karazam-pahoriana\r\nNy teninao nampody fifaliana\r\n\r\n;:;Ny omaly ny omaly tsy atao intsony\r\nNy omaly efa nilaozana\r\nNy androany ny androany hitoetra anilanao\r\nHadova ilay fiainana vaovao;:;\r\n\r\nAza ela fa miandry anao zahay\r\nAza ela fa mitady anao zahay\r\nEfa tsy tamana amin\'izao tontolo izao\r\nFa handova ilay fiainana vaovao\r\n\r\nNy omaly.....\r\nAza ela.....\r\nNy omaly...\r\n#Hir\'aina'),
(82, ':;: Andeha hiakatra hitsena :;:', ':;: Andeha hiakatra hitsena :;:\r\n:;: Hitsena \'lay famonjena :;:\r\nAvia tsenao \'lay Mpanjakanao\r\nFa avy Izy izao\r\n:;: Andeha hiakatra hitsena :;:\r\n:;: Hitsena \'lay famonjena :;:\r\nÃ” androm-pifaliana sy fihobiana\r\nEfa ela aho no niandry\r\nNo niandry Anao Jeso!\r\n\'Zao atsotrako ny sandry\r\nFa tonga Ianao Jeso!\r\nAdinoko avokoa, ireo ranomasoko\r\nÃ” androm-pifaliana sy fihobiana.\r\n:;: Trompetra no injay manako :;:\r\n:;: Fiderana tsy miato :;:\r\nNy lanitra no indro tonga ety\r\nRy tany mifalia!!!\r\n:;: Trompetra no injay manako :;:\r\n:;: Fiderana tsy miato :;:\r\nNy foko e mitroatra, fa faly loatra!!!'),
(83, 'Raha hipaika atoato  ALISON', 'Raha hipaika atoato \r\nilay ora izay hitsarana ahy\r\nHo tsiahivina avokoa\r\nIreo tantaram-piainako\r\nNa ny ratsy na ny soa\r\nMoa ve ho tafajoro\r\nKa ho hita tsy hanan-tsiny aho\r\nTohano aho Raiko o!\r\nHiatrika izany\r\n\r\nEfa mba nibebaka aho\r\nNatao batisa ihany koa\r\nF\'izany moa no baikonao\r\nHidirako any an-danitra\r\nNefa tsy azo antoka\r\nNy fahamarinako ry Ray\r\nKa mila ny \'lay Zanakao\r\nMba hisolo vava ahy\r\nFa Ianao Jeso no mendrika'),
(84, 'Vonivato Mamiko', 'Vonivato Mamiko\r\n\r\nMamiko ny ahatongavanao\r\nRy Jeso Mpanjaka tsitoha\r\nFahoriana ny ety!\r\nMankaleo mahakivy fo\r\nO!avia aza ela ianao\r\nHampitoetra fiadanana\r\nSy hamerina indray \r\nLay edena taloha efa very\r\n\r\nref:\r\nMoa ve mbola ho ela be \r\nIlay fiverenanao \r\nMiandry ireo zanakao\r\nEfa fantatrao\r\nMoa ve mbola ho ela be \r\nIlay fiverenanao \r\nMiandry ireo zanakao\r\nAz\' ela Jeso\r\n\r\n2)Fantatro f\'efa ela ianao\r\nRy Jeso no te handray ahy\r\nTsy tinao hoe very \r\nIzahay raha ho avy ianao\r\nO!avia aza ela ianao\r\nHampitoetra fiadanana\r\nSy hamerina indray \r\nLay edena taloha efa very\r\n\r\nref:\r\nMoa ve mbola ho ela be \r\nIlay fiverenanao \r\nMiandry ireo zanakao\r\nEfa fantatrao\r\nMoa ve mbola ho ela be \r\nIlay fiverenanao \r\nMiandry ireo zanakao\r\nAz\' ela Jeso\r\nAz\' ela Jeso'),
(85, 'Manana Finoana eh!', 'Miandry manantena tsy ho ela ny fiverenanao\r\nAoka samy hanontany tena hoe:vonona ve aho\r\nRaha anio ilay fotoana hisehoany\r\nIza re no ho faly sy ho tony\r\nFa tampotampoka,hantomotra sy ankatoka\r\n\r\n-Averiko foana e\r\nHo avy Jesosy\r\nManana finoana e\r\nHo avy tokoa(diovy ny fo)\r\n\r\nIreo famantarana dia marobe no efa mitranga\r\nGazety,onjam-peo,mampandre mandrangaranga\r\nNy baiboly efa ela no nilaza\r\nNy zavatra rehetra efa mazava\r\nKa azo antoka fa hantomotra sy hankatoka\r\n\r\nDieny mbola misy ny fotoana dia tapaho ny hevitrao\r\nAoka koa tsy hinohino foana hoe zao na izao\r\nZay voalaza sy voasoratra ihany\r\nNo hinoana sy ekena hatrany\r\nAza mafy hatoka,fa Jeso ho avy tampoka.'),
(86, '#DIOVY_AHO Ambatomanga', '#DIOVY_AHO\r\n\r\nEo ampelatananao tokoa no apetrako izao\r\nny fiainako ry Raiko na tsy mendrika ho Anao\r\nEfa fantatrao ny amiko tsy miafina Aminao\r\nNa mipetraka dia hitanao na mitsangana ihany koa\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nDiovy aho sasao madio ho mendrika Anao .Oh miangavy Anao\r\nTantano re ka mba Ianao\r\nNo antompianako ety\r\nDiovy aho sasao madio\r\nHo mendrika Anao \r\nOh miangavy Anao\r\nTantano re ka mba Ianao\r\nNo antompiainako ety\r\n\r\nNy talentako fiteniko ny fijery ihany koa\r\nRaiso izy ireo tantano\r\nMba hitera bokatsoa\r\nMiangavy Anao ry Raiko o\r\nMitoetra ato ampo \r\nAza avelanao ho irery aho\r\nMba ho zanakao doria\r\nRef:\r\n<b> AMBATOMANGA'),
(87, '#HARENAKO LOVA MIAMPITA', '#HARENAKO\r\n1) Tsy ho azonao antsaina ny hafaliana anatiko ao\r\nSatria tsy mba ivelany ihany toy ny anizao tontolo izao \r\nFa hafaliana avy ao anaty miorina tsy mety maty\r\nAmbony ny finoko an\'i Jeso\r\nNa hesorina amiko aza izay rehetra ananako\r\nRaha mbola velona aho izay ny ahy no tanako\r\nHarenako Jesosy tia fananako doria doria tsy misy atakaloko azy sanatria\r\n\r\n2) Hanontany angamba ia nao hoe fa dia nahoana indrindra re \r\nDia tsotra ihany no lazaiko ho valin izany teninao\r\nNy heloko dia nofafany ny gadrako dia novahany\r\nNy fiainako dia nohavaoziny\r\nIlay fiadanampony no indro fa nomeny ahy \r\nAry ny famimdrampony no injao mameno ny fanahy\r\nTsy misy raha ny toizao ny zavatra efa itanao\r\nTena ambony ny fitiavan Jeso\r\n\r\n3) Fanandramana ilaina hampitombona herimpo \r\nZay tsapa fa miha mirona latsaka ambany tokoa \r\nMila miarina raha lavo miankina amin\' Ilay Avo\r\nNanaiky ho faty tany Kalvary\r\nTsy ampy hery handresena ny ratsy nahazatra anao\r\nFa Jesosy famonjena no antoka hanampy anao\r\nDia eo ianao no miantoraha\r\nTeo aho no nanao fampitaha \r\nNy fitiavany tsy miova ho doria \r\n LOVA MIAMPITA'),
(88, '***SOA IHANY***(Njato sy Tafika)', '***SOA IHANY***\r\n(Njato sy Tafika)\r\n==========\r\nSoa ihany aho Jeso teo anilanao\r\nRaha niharan\'izao fitsapana izao\r\nFa raha ts\'izany angamba dia loza izay nanjo\r\nFa tena very hevitra aho\r\nSoa teo anilako ianao ho tokiko re\r\n\r\nSoa ihany aho Jeso nampahoriana\r\nHianarako ireo zay fitsipikao\r\nHampahendry ahy mihoatra noho ireo fahavaloko\r\nSatria ato anatiko sy efa ivelomako\r\nIreo didinao ho mandrakizay\r\n\r\nRef: F\'ao aminao dia ho maivana daholo ireo fakam-panahy\r\nSatria ianao no nitondra sy nilanja ireo mavesatray\r\nSady mahatoky sy marina,mamela ireo helokay\r\nTomoera Tompo Ã´ aty anatinay\r\nIanao\r\n(annnnn)\r\n\r\nSoa ihany aho Jeso nampahoriana\r\nHianarako ireo zay fitsipikao\r\nHampahendry ahy mihoatra noho ireo fahavaloko\r\nSatria ato anatiko sy efa hivelomako\r\nIreo didinao ho mandrakizay\r\n\r\nRef: F\'ao aminao dia ho maivana daholo...\r\nToa nofafanao ty fahadisoanay\r\nNodiovinao t@ ny ranao soa\r\n\r\nRef: F\'ao aminao dia ho maivana daholo...'),
(89, 'Faniriako Ray Ã´ ROHAMA', ':;:Faniriako Ray Ã´\r\n\r\nNy ho eo ankaikinao\r\nAnilanao mandrakizay\r\nArovy aho\r\nTantano fa sao mania\r\nNy herinao no tokiko:;:\r\nAza manahy fa tsy ho irery ianao\r\nHo anilanao mandrakizay\r\n\r\nHiaro anao hitantana anao koa \r\n(Lehilahy)ny heriko ho tokinao\r\n(Vehivavy)ny herinao ho tokiko\r\nNa sarotra izay aleha\r\n(Lehilahy)ny tanako ho tokinao\r\nVehivavy)ny tananao no tokiko\r\nAzoniko ka tsy avelako\r\n(Lehilahy)ny sandriko hiaro anao\r\n(vehivavy)ny sandrinao hiaro ahy\r\nFaniriako ray o....\r\nAza manahy...\r\n\r\nRef\r\nTsy ho irery aho fa\r\nHo eo anilanao\r\nHiaro anao ho tokinao\r\nTsy hisaraka aminao\r\nN\'aiza aleha \r\nIanao no malalako\r\nRef.na sarotr\'izay aleha...\r\nAzoniko ka tsy avelako\r\nIanao no malalako\r\nMpihira:Rohama'),
(90, '~~~Masoandro~~~ Efitra', '~~~Masoandro~~~\r\nIo lay masoandro mitondra azavana\r\nSy tara-pitiavana koa\r\nIo lay masoandro mitondra hafanana\r\nManaitra anao mba hifoha\r\nMizara ny soa sy tsara\r\nHitory sy hanambara\r\nHanao zay azo atao\r\nToetra miavaka tsy manavakavaka\r\nNa inona toeranao\r\n\r\nIo lay masoandro raha hilentika koa\r\nDia mbola mampanantena\r\nFa rahampitso hivimbina zavatsoa\r\nNy bitsik\'ilay taratra mena\r\nHizara ny soa sy tsara\r\nHitory sy hanambara\r\nHanao zay azo atao\r\nToetra miavaka tsy manavakavaka\r\nNa inona toeranao\r\n\r\nNa takona semban-drahona aza\r\nDia mibaliaka kosa any ambony\r\nMamiko loatra tiako ny milaza\r\nTsy hoe zay dia tsy hipoitra intsony\r\nF\'Hizara ny soa sy tsara\r\nHitory sy hanambara\r\nHanao zay azo atao\r\nToetra miavaka tsy manavakavaka\r\nNa inona toeranao\r\nEfitra'),
(91, 'Ny fanantenako  Choral Feon\' ny Fanantenana Ambohijafy. Adventiste Ambohijafy Eglise', 'Ny fanantenako\r\n\r\n1) Ny faratampon\' ny fanantenako dia izao,\r\nNy ahita maso lay mpanavotra ahy sy ianao.\r\nNy faratampon\' ny fifaliako dia izao.\r\nNy ahita maso lay tia ahy sy ianao.\r\n\r\n2) Rehefa hoavy tsy hoela,Eny andrahondanitra.\r\nJesosy Tompo lay mpanavotra ahy sy ianao.\r\nNy fahoriana,fijaliana,\r\nAmin\' izay ho tapitra,\r\nSambatra isika ao an danitra.\r\n\r\n( ref) Ho hitako tokoa re,\r\nAmin\' izay fotoana izay.\r\nNy tavan\' i Jehovah Ray.\r\nHo hitako tokoa re,\r\nAmin\' izay fotoana izay.\r\nJesosy fitiavana.\r\n\r\n3) Tsy hisy intsony ranomaso na fahafatesana.\r\nTsy hisy fangirifiriana na fanaintanana.\r\nFa efa Lasa avokoa,ireo zavatra taloha.\r\nHisolo paradisa tena soa.\r\n\r\n( ref) Ho hitantsika rehetra izao.\r\nAmin\' izay fotoana izay.\r\nNy tavan\' i Jehovah Ray.\r\nHo hitantsika rehetra izao.\r\nAmin\' izay fotoana izay.\r\nJesosy fitiavana.\r\n\r\nChoral Feon\' ny Fanantenana Ambohijafy. Adventiste Ambohijafy Eglise'),
(92, 'Amorony fo madio aho Amorony fo vaovao HANITR\'I KRISTY', 'Amorony fo madio aho\r\nAmorony fo vaovao\r\n\r\n1)O!Amorony fo vaovao aho\r\nFo vaovao tahaka ny Anao \r\nIriko indrindra Ray ny ho tahaka Anao\r\nO!Amorony fo vaovao\r\n\r\nRefrain:\r\n\'Reo toetrako taloha\r\nHomboiko avokoa\r\nAmbony hazo fijalianao ry Jeso Mpamonjy o!\r\nO!Mba ampio aho\r\nKa mba tohano fa tsy hefako irery \r\nIzao faniriako izao\r\n\r\n2)\'Reo lalandratsiko mahazatra ahy\r\n\'Reo fomba ratsy izay niainako\r\nTsy hiverenako,efa neniko tokoa\r\nO!Amorony fo vaovao\r\n\r\nRefrain:....\r\nAmorony fo madio aho\r\nAmorony fo vaovao\r\nHANITR\'I KRISTY'),
(93, 'RY JESO ZOKY GROUPE LALAO', 'RY JESO ZOKY\r\n\r\n1)Ry Jeso Zoky o!\r\nTaminao no nahavonjy anay\r\nFa efa latsaka tao anaty haizina\r\nRy Jeso Zoky o!\r\nMaminay ny Anaranao\r\nManadio anay mpanota Ianao\r\nJeso fitiavana\r\n\r\n2)Ry Jeso Zoky o!\r\nSitrakay ny hanome Anao\r\nIty fonay manontolo\r\nEny raiso ho tranonao\r\nNy andronay Jeso\r\nHo Anao mandrakizay\r\nManadio anay mpanota Ianao\r\nJeso fitiavana\r\nNy ratra nentinao\r\nSy ny latsa niharetanao\r\nNamela holatra\r\nMampiseho fitiavana\r\nRy Jeso Zoky o!\r\nTianay,malalanay\r\n(Manadio ny ota vitanay\r\nIanao,Jesosy o!)*2\r\nGROUPE LALAO'),
(94, '\'ZAHO HIANDRY ANAO Hanitri\'Kristy', '\'ZAHO HIANDRY ANAO\r\n\r\n1)Moa ny tany ve?No voahozona\r\nTsy hisy zava_mahasoa\r\nF\'izay rehetra mba alehanao\r\nToa fitaka avokoa\r\nFa torovana sady reraka\r\nIzany saina sy ny fo\r\nToa satriko hikopak\'elatrToa satriko hikopak\'elatra\r\nNefa mba ho aiza moa\r\n\r\nRef:\r\nFa miandry sy matoky ny fiverenanao\r\nTompo o!Na sarotra ny dia\r\nManantena ilay tany sy lanitra vaovao\r\nNa dia mafy aza ny ady ety\r\nTompo o!\'Zaho hiandryTompo o!\'Zaho hiandry Anao\r\nO!Ampio tsy ho potraka\r\nEny fa na haharitra\r\n\'Zaho hiandry Anao\r\n\r\n2)Raha ny heriko\r\nDia tsy afaka hisedra zava_tsarotra\r\nMangataka ny fanohananao\r\nMba tsy ho kivy aho\r\nFa tsy manana ianteherana\r\nAfa_tsy ilay sandrinao\r\nNy hany mba italahoako\r\nAmpaherezo aho'),
(95, '~~~~~MPITANTANA~~~~~ Balsama', '~~~~~MPITANTANA~~~~~\r\n\r\nIza moa no olona ety an-tany\r\nNo mahay mamantatra n\'a maminany\r\nZay rehetra tsara sy ilainy\r\nJamba aho Tompo Ã´ ka mila hatrany\r\n\r\nMpitantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro isan\'andro\r\nMpanafaka amin\'ny olana s\'y izay mety mahazo\r\nFa Ianao,Ianao Jeso no mahalala\r\nNa izay miafina,na tsy ambara\r\nIndrandray anie aho misalasala \r\nFa Ianao Jeso,Ianao tsy miala\r\nMitantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro, isanandro\r\nManafaka ny olana sy izay mety mahazo\r\nIanao\r\nIanao Jeso no Hery sy apingako\r\nKa tsy hanan-tahotra aho fa eo Ianao\r\n\r\nMitantantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro isanandro\r\nManafaka n\'y olana s\'y izay mety mahazo\r\nMitantana n\'y tanako isan\'andro isan\'andro\r\nKa dia misaotra anao satria Ianao efa ampy ho Ahy\r\nFa Ianao,Jeso Ianao tsy miala\r\n\r\nBalsama'),
(96, 'Sabata Jacqueline', 'Andro iray nomen\'i TOMPO\r\nAndro tokana tsy miova\r\nNohamasininy.\r\nNotahiany tena miavaka\r\nMba ho famantarana AZY\r\nIlay Mpamorona,\r\nDia nomeny ahy sy ianao\r\nMba ho fitsaharana,\r\nAry mbola hitoetra\r\nEny! Ho mandrakizay.\r\n\r\nIZY mihintsy no niteny \r\nNanao Sonia.\r\nIo no famantarana Amiko sy hianao\r\nMbola ho tsarovana\r\nEny! Na any an-danitra\r\nNY SABATA fitsaharana,\r\nTsy miova fa maharitra.\r\n\r\nGroupe Jacqueline'),
(97, 'Eo am - pelatananao Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa', 'Eo am - pelatananao Ny AmbasadÃ´rÃ  Ambasa\r\nClÃ©: Do\r\nO!O! O! O!( choeur)\r\n1.\r\nZay nataonao rehetra fantatro fa mahasoa\r\nFitiavan - tsy voafetra eny hatramin\'ny taloha\r\nO!O!O!O!\r\nRay fitiavana ianao mijery hatrany hatrany\r\nSy miahy ny fiainako\r\nRef:\r\nNa mandeha aho na miteotra hitanao avokoa\r\nNy miafina rehetra ( avec choeur)\r\nFantatraro ry Tsitoha O!O!O!\r\nNy fianako tontolo eo am- pelatananao!\r\nO!O! O! O!( choeur)\r\n2.\r\nNa ho mamy na mangidy ny andro sisa iainako\r\nTsy izaho no misafidy fa Ianao ry Tsitoha \r\nO!O!O!O!( choeur)\r\nRay fitiavana Ianao faniriako ao anaty\r\nTsy hisaraka aminao\r\nRef:\r\nNa mandeha aho na miteotra hitanao avokoa\r\nNy miafina rehetra ( avec choeur)\r\nFantatraro ry Tsitoha O!O!O!\r\nNy fianako tontolo eo am- pelatananao!\r\nRef:\r\nNa mandeha aho na miteotra hitanao avokoa\r\nNy miafina rehetra ( avec choeur)\r\nFantatraro ry Tsitoha O!O!O!\r\nNy fianako tontolo eo am- pelatananao!\r\nRay fitiavana Ianao \r\nNy fiainako tontolo\r\nEo am-pelatananao (avec choeur)\r\nO!O!O!O!O! ( avec choeur) \r\nEo am-pelatananao (duo miadana)'),
(98, 'Tsinjovy(Balsam)', 'Tsinjovy(Balsam)\r\n\r\n1_Tsinjovy anie ny lanitra\r\nMisy ireo voronkely marobe izay tsy mahay ny mamafy na mitahiry an_tsompitra re!\r\nFa ny Ray Tsitoha miahy azy\r\nKa dia tsy misy ahiany\r\nRef:koa nahoana ianao\r\nNo manahy ny ho avy\r\nMoa va tsy mino ny fonao\r\nFa omeny izay ilainao\r\n2_Zahao koa eny an-tsaha\r\nMisy ireo voninkazo marobe\r\nToy reny ny lisy,ny raozy koa\r\nMitafy lokon\'andriandehibe\r\nRef..\r\n3_dinihonao reo namanao\r\nIzay samy manana ny endriny\r\nSatria tsy iray ny fiaviny\r\nSamy hafa koa ny fisainany\r\nFa ny Ray Tsitoha sady mpiahy\r\ntsy manavaka fa mampiray\r\nRef..'),
(99, 'Ako farany OBEY', 'Ako farany OBEY\r\nGive me your O, O!\r\nGive me your B, B!\r\nGive me your E, E!\r\nGive me your Y, Y!\r\nAnd what\'s that\'s spelling?\r\nOBEY!!!!\r\nOh yeah!\r\nO B E Y\r\nobey your mum and dad\r\nO B E Y\r\nMakes them very glad\r\nListen to the words they say\r\nObey your parents every day\r\nO B E Y\r\nObey your mum and dad\r\n(one more time!)\r\nO B E Y\r\nObey your mum and dad....\r\n(OK, now here is something you can practice)\r\nWhen your riding in the car sing still (Sing still)\r\nWhen your mum says go to bed say I will (I will)\r\nWhen it\'s time to clean your room,\r\nyou must pick up your toys\r\nRemember that obey brings joy\r\n(Oh!)\r\nOBEY\r\nObey your mum and dad....\r\n(God loves it when you listen!)\r\nWhen mum and dada say tell the truth, don\'t lie (don\'t lie!)\r\nWhen they say you have an oath, don\'t cry (don\'t cry!)\r\n\'Cause when you do the things you should,\r\nyou\'ll find out it\'s true\r\nObey, n\'the end, is very good for you\r\n(oh!)\r\nO B E Y\r\nObey your mum and dad....\r\n(x2)\r\n(OBEY!!!!!!!!!!!!!)\r\nO B E Y\r\nObey your mum and dad....\r\nListen to the words they say\r\nObey your parents every day\r\nO B E Y\r\nObey your mum and dad!\r\n(Yeah, do it!\r\noh yeah!!!!)'),
(100, '***AOKA IZAY***', '***AOKA IZAY***\r\nAoka izay reo fanaratsiana\r\nEndrikendrika fomba fanao\r\nAoka izay fa tsy hanatsara ny fanahinao\r\nAmpy izay ny fifosafosana\r\nbitsibitsika ny namanao\r\nAoka izay aoka izay\r\nDia ovay re ny fomba fanao\r\n\r\nNgamba ianao tsy mahatsapa fa ireny\r\nDia mamono na dia hoe teny\r\nFa tena marary mandratra fo manimba tokoa\r\nTsy aleo ve teny mba mampahery\r\nMampitodika ireo mino very\r\nDia ho hitanao fa hamonjy azy ireo teny natao\r\n\r\nNdeha ialana reo hita fa ratsy\r\nFifankatiavana no hajoro\r\nAvelao any ireny fa toa mampikoro\r\nNy firaisana no aoka ho hita\r\nZay kinasa rehetra dia ho vita\r\nTsy ho ela dia io fa ho tody soa ny dia'),
